endpoints.description: The endpoint definitions to be called by the system for the following properties.

resource.description: The endpoint to retrieve a resource items

resources.description: The endpoint to retrieve a group of resource items that conform to the schema

ghost.description: provides detail information on how to query the GhoST system to return cached resources

mapping.description: describes how to map the normative schema structure to the payload returned by GhoST.  Will contain properties of the normative schema structure and values as mappings

query.description: the query string to retrieve the resource

propertyResolvers.description: An array of either expressions, mappings, or endpoints to return properties of the normative schema structure not returned as part of the resource endpoint calls

endpoint.description: the endpoint to call to return a payload that contains the property

expression.description: a regex expression to return the value for the property

mapping.description: describes how to return the value of the property based off a mapping of the returned payload

name.description: a property name as declared in the normative schema structure

schema.description: A schema to define the normative structure as required by the Console UI capabilities returned by the resource endpoint

type.description: an identifier for the resource type
